title: Ep. 1300 - Baldev Singh's Arrival Is Awaited - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bulbul tells the police that she is an adult and can take care of herself. Everyone waits for her parents to come.

title: Ep. 1301 - Baldev Accepts The Marriage - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Finally, Baldev accepts the newly married couple. Baldev announces that he will get them married in a grand way as he had wished for.

title: Ep. 1302 - Bulbul's Shocking Revelation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bulbul reveals to Popatlal that she loves someone else. Popatlal is shattered and sits down in despair. She apologizes to him.

title: Ep. 1303 - Heartbroken Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal requests everyone to postpone the marriage dates. Baldev asks Popatlal as why he is worried. He warns Popatlal that he better takes care of his daughter. Baldev is impressed with him.

title: Ep. 1304 - Popatlal's Marriage Preparation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is excited about Popatlal's marriage. They discuss the rituals and what happens after marriage

title: Ep. 1305 - Worrisome Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal worries if Rahul would have taken the flight. Everyone gathers at Popatlal's house and discuss their marriage stories

title: Ep. 1306 - Arrival Of Wedding Day - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham dances to their hear out in Popatlal's procession. Popatlal asks for Bulbul but Daya informs him that he won't get to see her until all the rituals are done.

title: Ep. 1307 - The Exchange Of Groom - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the rituals take place and everyone is happy that Popatlal is getting married. The couple takes everyone's blessings.

title: Ep. 1308 - Popatlal's Revelation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal explains everyone about his master plan. He tells that he had to take Tapu Sena and Abdul's help.

title: Ep. 1309 - Daya Misses Sunderlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya hands over the herbal drink to Jetha and asks him to drink it as that's good for health

title: Ep. 1310 - Jetha's Escape Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets to know that Sunder will be arriving soon so he plans to escape to his shop.

title: Ep. 1311 - Sunerlal's Jalsa Idea - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu is excited as Sunder has planned a Jalsa for everyone. Daya asks Jetha to leave for the clubhouse as everyone would have reached already. Jetha calls Taarak up and tells him not leave until he comes as he has something to discuss about.

title: Ep. 1312 - Sunder's New Scheme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha asks him about his plans. Sunderlal assures everyone that he will arrange it in a grand way that no one would have ever imagined. He takes a leave and tells them that he will go inform his friends and family in Ahmedabad about the celebration.

title: Ep. 1313 - Jethalal Messes Up - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka hands over the phone to Jetha and asks him to take the order. Jetha is worried and was thinking of Sunderlal so he shouts and the customer who was over the phone hears it and mistook his words. Jetha apologises to him.

title: Ep. 1314 - Tapu Sena Dances - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu Sena is all dressed up and dances as they are excited about the evening celebration. Tapu suggests Champaklal to wear something different to which he refuses. Gokuldham is amazed to see the unique decoration arranged by Sunder.
